.codrops-top.clearfix
  -# %span.right
    %a.menu-right.user-log
      %span Volver a mi perfil
  %span.right
    %a#back.menu-right.three
      %span Regresar
%header.bg-header.price
%section.contenido
  .container.no-padding
    .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.col-form-registry.price
      .row
        .col-xs-4.col-sm-1.col-sm-offset-9
          .progress-step.active
            %label 1
            %img{src: "/vendor/img/step1.png"}/
        .col-xs-4.col-sm-1
          .progress-step.active
            %label 2
            %img{src: "/vendor/img/step2.png"}/
        .col-xs-4.col-sm-1
          .progress-step
            %label 3
            %img{src: "/vendor/img/step3.png"}/
      %h1
        Servicio
        %strong Tailored
      %hr/
      .row
        .col-sm-12.col-boxtrip
          .row.center
            %h2
              %strong
            %h4.p-info
              %strong Boxtrip
              te ayuda
            %p
              Solo completa los siguientes datos y nosotros nos encargamos de ayudarte con tu mudanza. Para brindarte mayor seguridad de tus datos dale un vistazo a nuestro
              %strong
                %a.b-info{"data-target" => "#aviso", "data-toggle" => "modal", href: ""} Aviso de privacidad
          %hr/
          .row
            .col-sm-4
              .form-group
                %label Nombre:
                %input.form-control{type: "text"}/
              .alert.alert-info.alert-dismissible.alert-boxtrip{role: "alert"}
                %button.close{"aria-label" => "Close", "data-dismiss" => "alert", type: "button"}
                  %span{"aria-hidden" => "true"} ×
                %strong Warning!
                Better check yourself, you're not looking too good.
            .col-sm-4
              .form-group
                %label Apellido Paterno:
                %input.form-control{type: "text"}/
              .alert.alert-info.alert-dismissible.alert-boxtrip{role: "alert"}
                %button.close{"aria-label" => "Close", "data-dismiss" => "alert", type: "button"}
                  %span{"aria-hidden" => "true"} ×
                %strong Warning!
                Better check yourself, you're not looking too good.
            .col-sm-4
              .form-group
                %label Apellido Materno:
                %input.form-control{type: "text"}/
              .alert.alert-info.alert-dismissible.alert-boxtrip{role: "alert"}
